13:05:02Z","body":"Yeah ... note on [capturing the display](https://developer.apple.com/library/mac/documentation/GraphicsImaging/Conceptual/QuartzDisplayServicesConceptual/Articles/DisplayCapture.html):\n`Note: None of these drawing options require a window. Attempting to position a window over a captured display and draw into the window may be unsuccessful—or may present undesirable results such as illegible or invisible content—because of interactions between full-screen graphics and the graphics hardware.`\n\nSounds like doing the old full screen view path when set mode doesn't match the desktop is the required crappy solution -- even if rendering to a texture is preferred from the user's point of view.\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/62062813/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"SephiRok","id":686553,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY4NjU1Mw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/686553?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok","html_url":"https://github.com/SephiRok","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/6