ngl_contexts.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40001987-CH216-SW28).`\n\nDo you think maybe changing the back buffer size is something that would make sense for GLFW to do? I imagine it might cause issues for users, but there could be a parameter to disable the default behavior.\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/62147607/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"SephiRok","id":686553,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY4NjU1Mw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/686553?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok","html_url":"https://github.com/SephiRok","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SephiRok/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/comments/65318105","html_url":"https://github.com/glfw/glfw/issues/378#issuecomment-65318105","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/378","id":65318105,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDY1MzE4MTA1","user":{"login":"elmindreda","id":133714,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzcxNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/133714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda","html_url":"https://github.com/e